  "reference_number": "BEL0140",
  "remarks": "\nSvetlana Aleksandrovna BONDARENKO is an involved person under the Belarus (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following grounds: BONDARENKO is or has been responsible for, engaging in, providing support for, or promoting the repression of civil society or democratic opposition in Belarus and actions, policies or activities which undermine democracy or the rule of law in Belarus. \n",
